---
title: Braised Chinese Soy Chicken with Garlic Rice & Carrot Ribbon Salad
description: This braised chicken is like a one-way ticket to flavour town. Time is all you need to turn chicken drumsticks into this meltingly tender delight, soaking up sweet soy flavours for a warm and comforting meal. Serve it over rice to get the most out of that sauce, and throw on a sprinkle of fresh chilli if you're feeling adventurous!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
